{"tid":1482223,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"網上行完約 求續約+睇英超plan","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:45:48.000Z","uid":9226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9cd65ef5e026387501a7af8c3cbc5acfee2002","tid":1482223,"uid":9226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"f95e0fb8b3926321cff14d42773f7c66feb089dd","tid":1482223,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=bc6f30aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=bc6f30aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"1aec37fe3992d89d5208d1e037f5dc26c32ba0c5","tid":1482223,"uid":291619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"954058b56e7dda0a0330c54427ad0272cdfaf8d0","tid":1482223,"uid":228984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34ae7e89da502415c8d46bbd23617db0821f476d","tid":1482223,"uid":222212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f5e9c550546bb1bad5984bb2ee67c91b82b0355","tid":1482223,"uid":229098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed3d0d4c42831d81d112735427bbfa2eee6673ee","tid":1482223,"uid":75504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff83be49c1272431877abf9b94ebf6d95b690ac1","tid":1482223,"uid":252546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"116968da4b4b6b24bdc3a088c60de01e7583870f","tid":1482223,"uid":252546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4969b21a552b1fb4865d736d3c6f43a4b986e